---
title: Maple-Glazed Salmon with Orange-Arugula Salad and Wild Rice
description: Maple syrup is the ingredient that comes to mind when one talks about Canadian cuisine. This Canada Day, celebrate with our tasty combination of maple-glazed salmon, wild rice and a yummy arugula salad.
